ISLAMABAD, Jan 28 (APP): Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib said on Friday that passage of State Bank of Pakistan Amendment Bill was a victory of the government.
In a tweet, he said the opposition, had dreamed of no-confidence against the government, but its defeat on this bill was a no confidence against itself.
